						<div class="postbody">I made a game for the Atari 2600 that leans hard on flicker and color changes per frame called M.M.S.B.C. II<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://atariage.com/forums/topic/207626-mmsbc-2-done/">http://atariage.com/forums/topic/207626-mmsbc-2-done/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />It is very hard to manually figure out which colors will cause the least eye strain when combining every other frame.  It's not just a matter of type of display but overall response rate and color accuracy.  It's really a nightmare.</div>

